              <img 
                src="/images/cases/ikea.jpg" 
                alt="IKEA Store Display"
                class="w-full h-full object-cover"
              />
              <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/60 to-transparent"></div>
              <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 p-6">
                <span class="text-white text-sm font-medium bg-blue-600 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Retail</span>
                <h3 class="text-white text-xl font-bold mt-2">IKEA Store, Sweden</h3>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="p-6">
              <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">IKEA has enhanced its in-store customer experience with UNV's innovative display solutions, providing clear and engaging product information.</p>
              <a href="/cases/ikea-sweden" class="inline-flex items-center text-blue-600 font-semibold hover:text-blue-700">
